---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
import '../styles/blog.css';

const title = "About the Creators";
const description = "Learn about the team behind Best Spa Vietnam.";
---

<MainLayout title={title} description={description}>
  <article class="container mx-auto px-4 py-12 max-w-4xl">
    <div class="mb-8 text-center">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-4">About Best Spa Vietnam</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none blog-content">
      <p>Best Spa Vietnam is your ultimate guide to discovering the finest spas and wellness centers across Vietnam. Our mission is to help both locals and travelers find authentic, rejuvenating spa experiences while supporting local businesses and preserving Vietnam's rich wellness heritage.</p>

      <h2>Our Story</h2>
      <p>This project was born from a passion for Vietnamese street food and a desire to create a comprehensive resource for phở enthusiasts. We've mapped thousands of phở vendors across Vietnam, from hidden street carts to famous establishments, making it easier for everyone to discover these culinary treasures.</p>

      <h2>The Creators</h2>
            <p>Best Spa Vietnam was created by Tech Ops Asia, a team of wellness enthusiasts and technology professionals based in Vietnam. Our local expertise and technical innovation allows us to create comprehensive wellness guides that serve both locals and tourists.</p>
      <p>Our passion for Vietnamese cuisine has also led us to create <a href="https://bestbanhmivietnam.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Best Bánh Mì Vietnam</a>, a guide to the country's best bánh mì.</p>

      <h2>Our Technology</h2>
      <p>We use advanced mapping technology and data analysis to provide accurate, up-to-date information about spa and wellness centers. Our platform is continuously updated with new locations, reviews, and photos to ensure you have the most current information available.</p>

      <h2>Contact Us</h2>
      <p>Have a question or suggestion? We'd love to hear from you! You can reach our team at <a href="mailto:hello@techopsasia.com">hello@techopsasia.com</a>.</p>
    </div>
  </article>
</MainLayout> 